Stat View:

	Functionality goals:
		scrollable index of stat blocks to select from
		search bar for stat blocks
		seperate pane that shows in-depth "from the book" info about the selected stat block
		image for the stat block
		shorthand info pane (e.g shows ability scores and CR)
        control for adding a custom stat block
        control for adding an instance of a stat block to the combat view
        control for deleting CUSTOM stat blocks ONLY

	Aesthetic goals:
		make perty.
